headline: Lots Of Upside At Upmarket Apparel Brand Ralph Lauren, Overcoming Tariff Concerns
summary: Ralph Lauren proved itself with strong holiday sales, solid gross and net profit margins compared to its sector. See why I rate RL stock a buy.
